### Document Verification API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v1
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@documentId = YOUR_DOCUMENT_ID_HERE
@verificationCode = YOUR_VERIFICATION_CODE_HERE

### ==============================================
### 1. Create Verification for Document (Private)
### ==============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/verify/document/{{documentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 2. Get Verification Details by Document ID (Private)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/verify/document/{{documentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 3. Verify Document by Code (Public)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/verify/{{verificationCode}}

### ==============================================
### 4. Get QR Code for Verification (Public)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/verify/{{verificationCode}}/qrcode

### ==============================================
### 5. Download QR Code as PNG (Public)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/verify/{{verificationCode}}/qrcode?format=buffer&width=300

### ==============================================
### 6. Regenerate QR Code (Private)
### ==============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/verify/document/{{documentId}}/regenerate-qr
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 7. Get Verification Statistics (Admin)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/verify/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 8. Get Verification Statistics with Date Range (Admin)
### ==============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/verify/admin/stats?startDate=2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&endDate=2026-12-31T23:59:59.999Z
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### 9. Invalidate Verification Cache (Admin)
### ==============================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/verify/admin/{{verificationCode}}/cache
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ==============================================
### CURL Examples
### ==============================================

# Verify Document (Public)
# curl -X GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/verify/VER-ABC12345-1234567890ABCDEF

# Get QR Code (Public)
# curl -X GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/verify/VER-ABC12345-1234567890ABCDEF/qrcode

# Create Verification (Private)
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/verify/document/DOCUMENT_ID \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"

# Regenerate QR Code (Private)
# curl -X POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/verify/document/DOCUMENT_ID/regenerate-qr \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN"

# Get Stats (Admin)
# curl -X GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/verify/admin/stats \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"
